<section xmlns="https://code.dccouncil.us/schemas/dc-library" xmlns:codified="https://code.dccouncil.us/schemas/codified" xmlns:codify="https://code.dccouncil.us/schemas/codify" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <num>2-423.04</num>
  <heading>Statute of limitations.</heading>
  <text>Any person filing a claim or petition under <cite path="§2-421">§ 2-421</cite> shall file the claim or petition no later than 2 years after the date the person received a certificate of innocence as required by <cite path="§2-422|(a)|(3)">§ 2-422(a)(3)</cite> and <cite path="§2-422|(b)|(3)">(b)(3)</cite>.</text>
